Crown.creator: Bullish0x
Crown.lore: Bullish0x convinced the entire Tang Gang community that Crown is the most valuable trait in the collection. It wasn't luck—it was a masterclass in social engineering. Royal Club members don't sell; they set unreasonable prices and wait.

Piccolo Turban.creator: MoJuice
Piccolo Turban.lore: The rarest head trait in the collection, and it can ONLY appear on Alien Wojak bases. This is the Green Connection: Chia is green, Piccolo is green, money is green. Namekian royalty for those who understand.

Tiara.creator: Bullish0x
Tiara.lore: Crown's sister trait, created specifically for the queens of Tang Gang. Bullish0x didn't forget that royalty comes in all forms. If Crown is king energy, Tiara is queen energy.

Headphones.creator: MoJuice
Headphones.lore: The rarest head trait by count, and 69% landed on Monkey Zoo bases. This honors Monkeyzoo, the educator who teaches Tang Gang in the Twitter Spaces. The apes are always listening.

Military Beret.creator: TheStakerClass
Military Beret.lore: TheStakerClass founded ChiaPhunks—the OG Chia NFT collection. The beret is his signature, and ChiaPhunks face left. 'The beret stays on' isn't a suggestion; it's identity.

Fedora.creator: DegenWaffle
Fedora.lore: DegenWaffle created Neckbeard Punks, the cyberpunk gambling degens of Tang Gang. The Fedora is part of the Classic Neckbeard loadout. 'The blade has been studied' is the motto.

Wizard Hat.creator: High Council
Wizard Hat.lore: The High Council of Wizards is a Tang Gang community that takes magic seriously. Whiz nerds don't explain their methods—it just works. Pizza, pizza, pizza.

Ronin Helmet.creator: OrangeGooey
Ronin Helmet.lore: OrangeGooey created the Ronin collection—masterless samurai who answer to no one. 'Accept cookies' is his signature phrase, delivered with tough love and zero sugarcoating.

Pirate Hat.creator: MoJuice
Pirate Hat.lore: Pirates don't ask permission. They take what they can and give nothing back. The hat alone carries the energy of the high seas.

Clown.creator: ChiaPhunks tribute
Clown.lore: They called us clowns for buying JPEGs on a blockchain nobody heard of. We called it alpha. This trait honors everyone who got laughed at before they got rich.

Trump Wave.creator: MoJuice
Trump Wave.lore: Political meme culture immortalized on-chain. 'Make bags great again' transcends politics—it's about conviction in your portfolio.

Spikes.creator: MoJuice
Spikes.lore: Punk rock energy for the rebels of Tang Gang. Not everyone fits the mold, and Spikes wearers don't try to.

Super Saiyan.creator: MoJuice
Super Saiyan.lore: Dragon Ball Z tribute for the anime degens. When your portfolio pumps, you're not at your final form. Power level: over 9000.

Centurion.creator: MoJuice
Centurion.lore: Roman warrior energy for those in the trenches. Part of the Full Roman loadout. The empire didn't fall—it moved to crypto.

Piccolo Uniform.creator: MoJuice
Piccolo Uniform.lore: Only appears on Alien bases. When Piccolo removes the weighted training gear, game over. Full Piccolo holders are Namekian royalty—the rarest named combo in the collection.

El Presidente.creator: MoJuice for TheStakerClass
El Presidente.lore: Created specifically as a tribute to TheStakerClass. El Presidente wasn't elected—he was appointed by the blockchain. Benevolent dictatorship of the portfolio.

Bepe Suit.creator: Tom Bepe
Bepe Suit.lore: Tom Bepe organized the $BEPE movement, the most liquid memecoin on Chia. 'Orange is greater than green' is the battle cry. $BEPE will be on Coinbase first—mark it.

Straitjacket.creator: MoJuice
Straitjacket.lore: Part of the Asylum Patient combo. The market tried to break you with rugs, FUD, and panic sells. It failed. Now the straitjacket is a badge of honor.

Drac.creator: Dracattus tribute
Drac.lore: Honors Dracattus, the vampire dev who ships code at dawn while others sleep. Bloodline secured. The thirst for building never stops.

Viking Armor.creator: MoJuice
Viking Armor.lore: Vikings raided, conquered, and took what they wanted. In crypto, same energy. Part of the Full Viking loadout. Valhalla awaits the diamond hands.

Ronin.creator: OrangeGooey
Ronin.lore: OrangeGooey's Ronin collection tribute. Masterless samurai don't follow the crowd—they follow discipline. Full Ronin holders walk alone but walk strong.

Roman Drip.creator: MoJuice
Roman Drip.lore: Full Roman combo piece. The Roman Empire is a meme, but the grind is real. Those in the trenches understand.

Wizard Drip.creator: High Council
Wizard Drip.lore: High Council of Wizards tribute. Don't ask how the magic works—just trust the process. Full Wizard holders have Spell Room access.

Bepe Army.creator: Tom Bepe
Bepe Army.lore: Tom Bepe's infantry. $BEPE soldiers march in orange, not green. The army grows with every convert.

Chia Farmer.creator: MoJuice
Chia Farmer.lore: THE collection uniform. 'Farmed, not FOMO'd' is the Chia way. While others panic-bought, Chia Farmers plotted in silence. Plot secured.

Super Saiyan Uniform.creator: MoJuice
Super Saiyan Uniform.lore: Full Super Saiyan transformation complete. DBZ energy for those who power up when the market dips.

SWAT Gear.creator: MoJuice
SWAT Gear.lore: Full SWAT loadout piece. 'Breach and clear' is the mindset—find the alpha, execute the plan, don't hesitate.

Astronaut.creator: MoJuice
Astronaut.lore: 'To the moon' isn't just a meme—it's a destination. Astronaut on Moon combo holders already landed.

Pickle Suit.creator: MoJuice
Pickle Suit.lore: Rick & Morty tribute. 'I turned myself into a pickle' energy for the absurdist degens who don't take themselves too seriously.

Goose Suit.creator: Foods
Goose Suit.lore: Honors Foods, the Goose of Tang Gang. Gene Hoffman promised to honk on Joe Rogan's podcast. This is Tang Gang canon. Peace was never an option.

Gopher Suit.creator: Josh Painter
Gopher Suit.lore: Gophers are the official mascot of Chia. Josh Painter built the G4M economy around these little diggers. The gophers run the network.

Proof of Prayer.creator: Wojak meme
Proof of Prayer.lore: THE original Wojak pose. Hands together, eyes on the chart, praying the candle turns green. Every crypto holder has been here.

Leather Jacket.creator: ignoreart tribute
Leather Jacket.lore: Honors ignoreart, whose dank art everybody loves. The Leather Jacket is the uniform of those who let their work speak for itself.

VR Headset.creator: TheStakerClass
VR Headset.lore: TheStakerClass wears a VR Headset in his PFP. When the ChiaPhunks founder wears something, it becomes legendary. Already in the metaverse while others argue about it.

Wizard Glasses.creator: High Council
Wizard Glasses.lore: High Council of Wizards tribute. Spell Power vision lets you see alpha others miss. The glasses stay on.

Laser Eyes.creator: Bitcoin culture
Laser Eyes.lore: Remember when all of crypto Twitter had laser eyes? Pure conviction visualized. Diamond hands don't blink.

Clown Nose.creator: ChiaPhunks
Clown Nose.lore: Full Clown combo piece. ChiaPhunks tribute for those who embraced being called clowns. Honk if you're winning.

MOG Glasses.creator: Tang Gang
MOG Glasses.lore: Tang Gang signature accessory. When the MOG Glasses go on, the conversation is over. You've been mogged. No further discussion needed.

Fake It Mask.creator: Wojak meme
Fake It Mask.lore: The classic 'I'm fine' Wojak—smiling on the outside, crying on the inside. Portfolio down 80%? 'I'm fine.' The most relatable trait in the collection.

Cyber Shades.creator: DegenWaffle & OrangeGooey
Cyber Shades.lore: Two Tang Gang legends combined into one accessory. DegenWaffle's cyberpunk aesthetic meets OrangeGooey's style. A flex of community knowledge.

Hannibal Mask.creator: MoJuice
Hannibal Mask.lore: Asylum Patient combo piece. 'Silence of the degens' energy. You've gone too far down the rabbit hole—and you'd do it again.

Vampire Teeth.creator: MoJuice
Vampire Teeth.lore: Full Vampire combo with Drac outfit. Vampires hunt while others sleep. The thirst is real—for alpha, for gains, for victory.

Neckbeard.creator: DegenWaffle
Neckbeard.lore: DegenWaffle's signature trait. 'Winners win, and winners don't shave.' The Neckbeard is monetary policy—never trim, never sell.

Gold Teeth.creator: MoJuice
Gold Teeth.lore: Mouth full of profit. You don't get Gold Teeth by accident—every tooth represents a win. Already made it, already showing it.
